# Regulator

The purpose of a regulator is to

1. Provide a costant [[61-Archive/20220318120826-voltage|voltage]] to the [[61-Archive/20220221170305-battery|Battery]]-operated system
2. To provide different voltages to different parts of a system

> [!example]
> If you have a 12V [[61-Archive/20220223192844-power|Power]] supply for a specific component, but another component can only have 5V, then you can use a regulator, else, you may need two [[61-Archive/20220223192844-power|power]] supplies.
